  "text": "Meta-analysis was done using a standard program for the Peto method as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . An estimate of heterogeneity by χ 2 was calculated to determine if different studies could be combined, and a pooled estimate of the odds ratio, 95% confidence intervals, and two-tailed p-value was generated.",
